# Bookstore Management System (SQL Project)

## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview
The Bookstore Management System is a database-driven project developed using PostgreSQL.  
It focuses on designing a relational database, importing book data, and performing various SQL operations for data management and analysis.

This project demonstrates practical SQL skills such as table creation, data insertion, querying, and handling real-world database issues.

